test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert -9025 == -95
 +  where -9025 = <built-in function prod>([-5, -19, -95])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (0 == 3)
 +  where 0 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x75f566e62540>([-95])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x75f566e62540> = [[1, -95], [1, -95, 1], [-95, 1], [-95, 1, -95], [1, -95], [1, -95, 1], ...].count
